    61405 [label="HitachiOpenLicense:\nThis license is an addition to the terms of the GNU General Public License\nVersion 3: it is subject to the terms of the GNU General Public License Version\n3, and to the terms of this license. This license is subject to the terms of the\nGNU General Public License Version 3, and the terms of this license. The GNU\nGeneral Public License Version 3 is here:\nhttps://factbook.soft.hitachi.co.jp/production/db/legl_licenses/7"
